#

Simple Fried Fish

25 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

FishEggs

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-Free OptionHigh Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickFried

Description

Crispy, golden fried fish that's quick and delicious! Perfect for a weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • white fish fillets (like cod or tilapia): 1 pound
  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • cornmeal: 1/2 cup
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • egg: 1
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • vegetable oil: for frying
